<headline>Evacuation Immediate issued April 04 at 7:12PM CDT  by NWS Amarillo</headline>
<description>THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE
AMARILLO OFFICE OF EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT.
A MANDATORY EVACUATION ORDER HAS BEEN PUT IN PLACE FOR ALL AREAS
NORTH OF GIVENS AVENUE AND WEST OF HIGHWAY 287 DUE TO EXTREME
WILDFIRE BEHAVIOR. RESIDENTS ARE INSTRUCTED TO HEAD SOUTH TOWARDS
AMARILLO. A SHELTER HAS BEEN DESIGNATED AT RIVER ROAD HIGH SCHOOL IN
THE GYM.</description>
